The paper proposes a novel recommendation framework based on deep reinforcement learning, which involves modeling the interactions between users and recommender systems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CY).
